    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER RT-610 SERIES - INSTALL - COMPANION FLANGE OR YOKE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="1">
        <title>COMPANION FLANGE OR YOKE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lock the transmission by engaging two gears with the mainshaft sliding clutches.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Make sure the speedometer gear washer and the speedometer gear or replacement spacer are
                installed on the output shaft.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the companion flange on the splines of the tailshaft.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the companion flange nut. Tighten bolts to 400 to 450 ft-lbs. (542 to 610 N&#183; m)
                (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13024h6">Figure 176</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13024h6" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13024h6" filename="../figg13/g13024h6.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 176. Install Companion Flange Nut</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
